Need to install and add latexmk to path

Need to add gmail api stuff, install these python modules i guess? 
 pip install --upgrade google-api-python-client google-auth-httplib2 google-auth-oauthlib
(Sourced from https://developers.google.com/gmail/api/quickstart/python)

Install jinja2
 pip install jinja2
or smth

Create a desktop OAuth Client ID
https://developers.google.com/workspace/guides/create-credentials#oauth-client-id
Download as json, and rename to credentials.json

